The entity, enums, and service were created in earlier tasks. The VO and RO follow existing project patterns - see `BasePageRo` at `core/ro/BasePageRo.java` (has `pageNum` and `pageSize` fields). The `LongToStringSerializer` is used for long-to-string JSON serialization (see `UserSimpleInfoVo`). `getUserByIds` is available on `IApitableGrpcClientService`.

